race.comment: BRUTAL GLORY (7) resumes with Rodd sticking from a soft trial. Maps to advantage and races well at this track. Has the ability and with the two fancied ones scratched he comes right into it. PUREZZA (1) just missed before delivering a CL3 at Toowoomba as expected. Has a handy 2kg claim today and will run along from an inside gate. She is sure to give a big sight. VIALE (11) resumes and has switched stables. Just missed at Ballina heavily bet at her last fresh run and has trialled well. Has the ability and on song is a winning hope. GALPIN (8 ) has switched from a Victorian stable on a 202 day return. Will race over further but has shown enough to keep well onside.
